    "text": "Bangladesh is a South Asia country with a DC-type pension system centred on the General Provident Fund (GPF) \u2013 Civil Servants. The system includes 2 schemes: General Provident Fund (GPF) \u2013 Civil Servants, Civil Service Pension Scheme (Non-Contributory DB). The normal retirement age is 59 for both men and women. Contributions total 35.0% of insurable earnings (10.0% employee, 25.0% employer).",
